Madge Stuart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Madge_Stuart 0 Madge Stuart (5 August 1895 Holmesfield, Derbyshire - 10 October 1958, Monte Carlo, Monaco) was a British actress of the silent era. She married Dion Titheradge in 1928. Madge_Stuart ( 5_August_1895_Holmesfield , Derbyshire - 10_October_1958 , Monte_Carlo , Monaco ) was a_British_actress of the_silent_era .
